<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>192</hymn_number>
<aka>JESUS, LOVER OF MY SOUL</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu, ka tha Hehpihpa,
 Na angsung ah ei humin;
 Tui a hung kinawk tienga
 Huihpi a hung hat tieng leh;
 Ei selin, ei Hukdampa,
 Damsung huihpi a beih man;
 Lawng chawlhna mun ei tunin,
 Nangin ka thagau pawmin.

[V2]
 2. Mundang belhding ka nei puoi,
 Ka thagau Nangah kinga;
 Aw, keingawn ei nusie ki'n,
 Ei tungding ei lungmuon in;
 Ka kinepna pen Nangmah,
 Panpihna Nangah ka mu'i;
 Lieh ding bei ka lu khuh in,
 Nangmah tha lim nuom tak chun.

[V3]
 3. Krista, Nang na hi ka deih,
 Ka bangcheng Nangah ka mui;
 A puk a gim phawng dingin,
 Damlo hihdam in, pui in;
 Na min a dik a thiengtho,
 Kei diklohna'n ka dim hi;
 Mawhna, gitlohna' ka dim,
 Thutak, hehpihna'n Na dim.</lyrics>
<title>Isu, ka tha Hehpihpa</title>
</song>